      </p>
      <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
        </svg>
        Call 754-215-2272
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Content -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-16">

      <!-- General Questions -->
      <div>
        <div class="border-b-2 border-[#0f2a4a] pb-2 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a]">General Questions</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- What Is Mobile Car Detailing? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">What Is Mobile Car Detailing?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Mobile car detailing is a professional cleaning and reconditioning service that comes directly to your location. We bring all water, power, equipment, and premium products to your home, office, or anywhere in Fort Lauderdale so you get dealership-quality results without leaving your driveway.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Unlike a traditional car wash where you wait in line and drive through an automated tunnel, mobile detailing is a hands-on process performed by trained professionals. Every surface is cleaned, conditioned, and protected by hand using <a href="https://www.chemicalguys.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Chemical Guys</a> products and professional-grade tools.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Mobile detailing saves you time, delivers better results than automated washes, and eliminates the risk of swirl marks caused by dirty tunnel brushes. See our full list of <a href={`${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">car detailing services in Fort Lauderdale</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- How Does Mobile Car Detailing Work? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Does Mobile Car Detailing Work?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>You call or text us at 754-215-2272 to schedule a time. We arrive at your chosen location with our fully equipped mobile unit carrying fresh water, eco-friendly cleaning solutions, and professional-grade tools. We detail your vehicle on-site and notify you when your car is ready.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              The process is simple: choose your <a href={`${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">package</a>, tell us your vehicle type and location, and pick a date. We handle the rest. Our mobile unit is completely self-contained, so you don't need to provide water, power, or anything else.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Most clients go about their day while we work. We text before-and-after photos when the job is done, so you can see the transformation even if you're not on-site.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- What Areas Do You Serve? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">What Areas Do You Serve in South Florida?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>We serve Fort Lauderdale, Dania Beach, Hollywood, Pompano Beach, and surrounding Broward County communities. Our mobile detailing unit travels throughout South Florida so you never need to drive to a detail shop. We operate Monday through Saturday, 8 AM to 8 PM.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Whether you're at home in Victoria Park, at work downtown, or parked at a condo in Pompano Beach, we come to you. Our service area covers the major Fort Lauderdale neighborhoods and nearby cities where South Florida's climate demands regular vehicle care.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Not sure if we cover your area? Call us at <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">754-215-2272</a> and we'll let you know right away.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing & Packages -->
      <div>
        <div class="border-b-2 border-[#0f2a4a] pb-2 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a]">Pricing & Packages</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- How Much Does It Cost? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Much Does Mobile Car Detailing Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Our packages start at $50 for a <a href={`${base}quick-wash-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Quick Wash</a> on sedans. The <a href={`${base}fresh-start-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Fresh Start</a> runs $80-$110, and the <a href={`${base}complete-clean-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Complete Clean</a> runs $130-$160. Pricing varies by vehicle size — sedans, SUVs, and trucks each have separate rates.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Every package includes a professional hand wash, tire and rim cleaning, and window cleaning. Higher-tier packages add services like tire dressing, dashboard and console detailing, trunk cleaning, and fender well cleaning. View all packages and compare features on our <a href={`${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">pricing page</a>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We also offer individual add-on services like <a href={`${base}car-waxing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">car waxing</a>, <a href={`${base}clay-bar-treatment-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">clay bar treatment</a>, and <a href={`${base}leather-conditioning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">leather conditioning</a> that can be added to any package for targeted protection.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Discounts for Regular Customers? -->
