            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Do You Offer Discounts for Regular Customers?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Yes, we value loyal customers and run seasonal promotions throughout the year. We offer special pricing for clients who schedule recurring appointments and periodic discounts on popular packages. Contact us at 754-215-2272 to ask about our current promotions and repeat customer benefits.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Scheduling regular details every 3-4 months is the best way to maintain your vehicle's appearance and protect your investment. Consistent customers often see their vehicles hold more resale value because paint, leather, and trim stay in better condition over the years.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We also appreciate referrals. When you send friends or family our way, ask us about referral benefits when you book your next appointment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Services -->
      <div>
        <div class="border-b-2 border-[#0f2a4a] pb-2 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a]">Services</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- What Is Included in a Full Detail? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">What Is Included in a Full Detail?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>A full detail includes thorough exterior <a href={`${base}hand-wash-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">hand washing</a>, <a href={`${base}tire-dressing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">tire and rim cleaning with dressing</a>, fender well cleaning, window cleaning inside and out, <a href={`${base}dashboard-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">dashboard and console wipe down</a>, floor mat cleaning, and a complete <a href={`${base}interior-vacuuming-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">interior vacuum</a> including the trunk.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Our <a href={`${base}complete-clean-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Complete Clean</a> package covers every visible surface of your vehicle. We use the two-bucket wash method to prevent swirl marks, clean each wheel by hand, dress the tires for a deep black finish, and meticulously wipe down every interior surface.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              For even deeper cleaning, our <a href={`${base}premium-refresh-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Premium Refresh</a> adds interior shampooing, <a href={`${base}steam-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">steam cleaning</a>, and door jamb detailing for a like-new transformation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- How Long Does a Full Detail Take? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Long Does a Full Car Detail Take?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>A <a href={`${base}quick-wash-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Quick Wash</a> typically takes 30-45 minutes, a <a href={`${base}fresh-start-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Fresh Start</a> takes about 60-90 minutes, and a <a href={`${base}complete-clean-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">Complete Clean</a> takes 2-3 hours depending on vehicle size and condition. Heavily soiled vehicles may require additional time.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              We don't rush through your vehicle. Professional detailing takes time because every surface is cleaned by hand. Larger vehicles like SUVs and trucks naturally take longer due to the additional surface area. Vehicles that haven't been detailed in a long time or have heavy pet hair, sand, or stains may also need extra attention.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              When you book, we'll give you an accurate time estimate based on your specific vehicle and chosen package so you can plan your day accordingly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Engine Bay Cleaning -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Do You Offer Engine Bay Cleaning?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Yes, engine bay cleaning is available as an add-on to any package. We use safe degreasers and controlled steam to remove grime, grease, and road buildup from your engine compartment without risking damage to sensitive electrical components. A clean engine bay also helps you spot leaks early.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              In Florida's heat, grease and road grime bake onto engine surfaces quickly. Regular engine bay cleaning prevents buildup that can trap heat and mask potential mechanical issues. It also makes your vehicle look thoroughly maintained if you're preparing for a sale or inspection.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Ask about adding engine bay cleaning when you book your next <a href={`${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">detailing appointment</a>. Call <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">754-215-2272</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Smoke Odor Removal -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Can You Remove Smoke Odor from a Car?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Yes, we offer professional <a href={`${base}smoke-odor-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">smoke odor removal</a> using deep interior cleaning, <a href={`${base}steam-cleaning-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">steam treatment</a>, and odor-neutralizing products that eliminate tobacco and other smoke smells at the molecular level rather than simply masking them with fragrances.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Smoke particles embed deeply into fabric, carpet, headliners, and even plastic surfaces. A single air freshener won't solve the problem. Our <a href={`${base}odor-removal-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">odor removal process</a> involves thorough <a href={`${base}carpet-shampooing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">carpet shampooing</a>, <a href={`${base}seat-shampooing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">seat shampooing</a>, and steam treatment to extract embedded particles.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Severe smoke odor from years of tobacco use may require multiple treatments for complete elimination. We'll assess the situation and give you an honest recommendation during booking.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scheduling & Logistics -->
      <div>
        <div class="border-b-2 border-[#0f2a4a] pb-2 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a]">Scheduling & Logistics</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- How Do I Book? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Do I Book an Appointment?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>Booking is easy. Call or text us at <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">754-215-2272</a>, or email <a href="mailto:contact@route95mobilecardetailing.com" class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">contact@route95mobilecardetailing.com</a>. Tell us your vehicle type, preferred package, location, and ideal date. We confirm your appointment quickly and same-day availability is often possible.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              We recommend booking at least a day in advance for guaranteed availability, especially on weekends. However, we frequently have same-day openings during the week. Let us know your schedule and we'll find a time that works.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Visit our <a href={`${base}contact/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">contact page</a> for all the ways to reach us, or browse our <a href={`${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-[#0f2a4a] font-semibold hover:text-[#c0c7cf]">packages</a> to decide which service is right for your vehicle.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Water or Electricity? -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">Do You Need Access to Water or Electricity?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              <strong>No. Our mobile unit carries its own fresh water supply and all necessary equipment. We are fully self-contained, so we can detail your vehicle in a parking garage, office lot, driveway, or anywhere you park. You do not need to provide anything at all.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              This is one of the biggest advantages of our mobile service. You don't need to run an extension cord or connect a hose. Our unit is designed to operate independently so we can reach you wherever your vehicle is parked.
